      <title>法国总理挺过不信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/french-premiere-survives-no-confidence-vote-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数月的政治动荡，法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁周三挺过了不信任动议，确保通过 2025 年预算。彭博新闻社的 Alan Katz 报道了这一消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/french-premiere-survives-no-confidence-vote-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 18:54:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
